data.description: Charming Craftsman House with the perfect marriage of the 1920's and today's modern conveniences. Open kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Beautifully restored wood floors in the light and bright living area. Tall energy efficient windows, with decorative lighting and window coverings. Updates galore with central heat & air. Large front porch for relaxing in the cool evenings. This is an adorable rental home to call your own. Pet friendly and Just minutes away from Historic Downtown Denison.
